        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 4 at 1:41AM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 141 AM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Reagan County Airport, or near Big Lake, moving northeast at 55 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Big Lake and Reagan County Airport.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
